antly building and updating him)\n\n**Key concept:** Instead of one messy chat for everything, he uses **separate channels per project**, so everything stays organized and documents/pins are saved at the top of each channel.\n\n**Then he shows how to set it all up:**\n- Create a private Discord server\n- Tell OpenClaw to walk you through adding it as a bot\n- Create project channels\n- Set up automated workflows\n\nHe says this reduced his content creation research from **3 hours down to 5 minutes**.\n\nWant me to keep going through the next oldest video?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3783,"output":498,"cacheRead":41536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45817,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777687406135,"responseId":"06448e6e4d2d9cbb55b057d124a93fe4"}}
